```

Time:

As opportunities appear.

---

## Phase 4 — Exposure Control

When a trade triggers:

Run:

```text
Active Exposure Engine
```

Determine:

```text
Keep

Cancel Other Pending Orders

Reduce Concentration
```

---

## Phase 5 — Management

Review:

```text
Pressure

Environment

Alignment

Exposure
```

Manage live trades.

