# MASTER PRINCIPLE

The entire architecture can be summarized in one sentence:

```text
Macro finds opportunity.

Charts validate opportunity.

Execution finds entry.

Exposure controls risk.

Management protects capital.
```

That is the bird's-eye view of the current GCFIOS Trading Operating Architecture. It gives you the entire project on one page while preserving the logic of every module and where each module fits in the decision chain.
